data.description: Charming 3/2 single story home nestled on a spacious 0.67 acre lot in a tranquil, quiet neighborhood. This delightful property boasts an above ground swimming pool, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the outdoors. The home features a new roof installed in 2023, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. Additionally, a hot tub offers a luxurious retreat right in your own backyard. The property also includes a negotiable storage shed equipped with electricity and interior lighting, providing ample space for storage or a workshop. The kitchen and bathroom floors were updated in 2023, adding a fresh and modern touch to the home. In 2022, updates including paint, carpet, a concrete patio, electrical improvements, pool maintenance, hot tub servicing, deck maintenance, and landscaping enhancements were completed, ensuring that this home is move-in ready and offers a fantastic blend of comfort and style. A firepit provides the perfect setting for outdoor gatherings and relaxation.
